@startuml
title TCP Echo (Client ↔ Server)

actor Client
participant Server

Client -> Server : TCP connect()
Server --> Client : accept()

loop 메시지 송수신 (사용자가 q 입력 전까지)
  Client -> Server : send("hello")
  Server --> Client : send("Echo: hello")
end

Client -> Server : close()
Server --> Client : close()

note right of Server
TCP 특징:
- 연결 지향(3-way handshake)
- 순서 보장 / 재전송
end note
@enduml